          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "So, who is Fleuriation?",
            "faq_des": "<p>Fleuriation is more than just skincare—it's a faith-driven herbal wellness brand inspired by Genesis 1:29. Every product is handcrafted in small batches using high-quality organic and natural ingredients to restore and nourish your body while maintaining complete transparency about what goes into every formula.</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--16736981942590__9ad78513-f48a-4eed-affd-30f6d370be1c-1666772143a4c26d1e-1": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "What does Fleuriation mean?",
            "faq_des": "<p>The name combines the French word <em>fleuri</em> (meaning flowery or blooming) with the suffix <em>-ation</em>, representing the process of blooming naturally through herbs and plants.</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--16736981942590__9ad78513-f48a-4eed-affd-30f6d370be1c-1666772143a4c26d1e-2": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "What makes your products different?",
            "faq_des": "<p>Our products are herbal and plant-powered, non-toxic, safe for the whole family, handcrafted in small batches for freshness, and made with complete honesty about every ingredient we use.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_Gp4xRt": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Are your products safe for sensitive skin?",
            "faq_des": "<p>Yes. Our formulas are gentle, non-toxic, and free from synthetic ingredients and artificial fragrances. Our products are thoughtfully crafted with carefully selected ingredients for gentle, everyday care. Because every individual's skin is unique, we recommend performing a patch test before using any new product to help identify potential sensitivities or allergic reactions.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_whxPcf": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Are your products vegan and cruelty-free?",
            "faq_des": "<p>We never test on animals and offer several vegan products. Products containing beeswax are clearly labeled, and all beeswax is ethically sourced by local beekeepers.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_VKF9cb": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Do you use synthetic preservatives or additives?",
            "faq_des": "<p>No. We avoid synthetic fillers, parabens, sulfates, and unnecessary additives, using natural preservatives whenever needed.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_DHXyEN": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "What kind of ingredients do you use?",
            "faq_des": "<p>We use carefully selected botanical oils, medicinal herbs, and essential oils—including rosehip, calendula, chamomile, lavender, frankincense, and more—to nourish and restore healthy skin.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_8hK2Lp": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Is Fleuriation just about skincare?",
            "faq_des": "<p>No. Our mission goes beyond skincare to promote overall wellness while sharing the restorative benefits of medicinal herbs.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_J7mQzX": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Can I use these products on my kids?",
            "faq_des": "<p>Yes. We offer several gentle herbal products designed for children. Because every individual's skin is unique, we recommend performing a patch test before using any new product to help identify potential sensitivities or allergic reactions.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_P4vDnR": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "How do you make sure your products are high-quality?",
            "faq_des": "<p>We source ingredients from trusted suppliers and farmers who share our commitment to purity, sustainability, and ethical practices. Every product is handcrafted in small batches for maximum freshness.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_A9cLmW": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "How long do your products last?",
            "faq_des": "<p>We recommend using our products within 6–12 months and storing them in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_M2rTyE": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Do you offer wholesale?",
